en:
@realAbbowser: Have you set up the chests in those levels?
@recruitZ: Sorry, the progress is 20% behind schedule due to a lack of manpower.
@realAbbowser: How can this be? I sent you ten minions!
@recruitZ: Five of them were sent to the hospital after joining the New Black Shores. Three of them went to confess to the Primus in the Order of the D and never returned. You sold the last two to the Montellis.
@realAbbowser: Wait, so you're doing 10 guys' jobs? Are you a human Echo?
@realAbbowser: No, I mean, just quit all these excuses. You should work more proactively!
@realAbbowser: I haven't even brought up that giant Chest Mimic you set up that bit me! You'll be cooked if you screw up again!
@recruitZ: Okay.

@realAbbowser: Hey, you! Have you finished it?
@recruitZ: At the current pace, we should be able to finish the work on schedule. However, some of the given materials are missing, such as Cube snacks and cakes.
@realAbbowser: H-how could they be missing?
@recruitZ: Everything was complete when I took inventory. Someone might have been stealing a bite. We can check the surveillance video.
@realAbbowser: No! Don't check the videos! If they're missing, they're missing. Sort this out yourself!
@recruitZ: Okay.

@realAbbowser: Hey, all set? {Male=He;Female=She}'s gonna be here any minute.
@recruitZ: The job is done. Everything goes as planned.
@realAbbowser: Noice. Now get to my side quickly!
@recruitZ: Okay. I'll figure out a way to get there.
